devdoc.details: Pool that tracks shares of an underlying token, of which are deposited into COMPOUND. Earnings from provider is sent to recipients

balanceCompound().details: Get balance of COMP cToken in this pool

balanceCompoundInUnderlying().details: Get balance of compound token in this pool converted to underlying

balanceInUnderlying().details: Get balance of underlying token in this pool     Should equal to withdraw fee unless underlyings are sent to pool

calcPoolValueInUnderlying().details: Calculate total underlying balance of this pool     Total balance of underlying = total provider underlying balance (deposit + interest accrued) + withdraw fee

calcUndispensedEarningInUnderlying().details: Calculate outstanding interest earning of underlying token in this pool     Earning = total provider underlying balance - total deposit

calcUndispensedProviderReward().details: Get outstanding reward token in pool

params._compound: Compound cToken address for underlying token
params._underlyingToken: The underlying token thats is earning interest from provider

params._beneficiary: Address to benefit from the deposit

params._account: User for which to retrieve balance

params._beneficiary: Address to benefit from the withdraw
